INSERT INTO `books_hotels` VALUES (5,'Hotels in Rome','<div><span>You can book hotel of any category with us. Below are indicated rates for hotels in different seasons</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for 5* hotel - from 500 euro to 250 euro per room per night</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for 4* hotel - from 300 euro to 200 euro per room per night</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for 3* hotel - from 200 euro to 150 euro per room per night</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for mini hotels and appartment rent - from 150 euro to 80 euro per night</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>High season in Rome: 1 March - 30 October</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended 5* hotels:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">The Westin Excelsior </span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Veneto, 125</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.excelsior.hotelinroma.com/\"><span>www.excelsior.hotelinroma.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel Westin Exelsior in&nbsp;Rome has the reputation of a fantastic place. It has famous Doney restaurant. There is the fitness centre and&nbsp;also massage centre.&nbsp;The location is on legendary Via Veneto just few steps from Piazza di Spagna and Villa Borgese</span></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"IT\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Majestic Roma </span></span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Vittorio Veneto, 50</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelmajestic.com\"><span>www.hotelmajestic.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>One of the best hotels located on Via Veneto. It was open in 1889 next to Villa Ludovisi palace. Just few steps walk to Villa Borgese, Spanish steps, via Condotti with elegant shops</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Splendid Royal</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via di Porta Pinciana, 14</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.splendidroyal.com/\"><span>www.splendidroyal.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>It is a boutique hotel located in wonderful historic place that was built in 1880. Near the prestigious district of Via Veneto and Spanish steps, near Villa Borgese park. Very elegant interior with fire places, antique furniture and original paintings. Mosaic marble floor, chandeliers, flowers make a really special atmosphere of this hotel. Mirabelle restaurant is the Michelin restaurant</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Rome Cavalieri Hilton </span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Cadlolo,101</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.romecavalieri.com\"><span>www.romecavalieri.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Location of the hotel is very special - few minutes trip from Piazza di Spagna district. It is located 35 kilometres from Fiumicino airport. The hotel is located on top of Monte Mario hill - with unique view to all Rome. There is huge spa centre and swimming pool.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Grand Hotel Parco dei Principi </span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Frescobalsi,5</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.parcodeiprincipi.com\"><span>www.parcodeiprincipi.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is located in the Villa Borgese area, 10 minutes walk from Via Veneto. It was recently restored. Pauline Borgese restaurant is considered to be one of the best in Rome</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Aldrovandi Palace Hotel</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Ulisse Aldrovandi, 15</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.aldrovandi.com\"><span>www.aldrovandi.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is located in one of most prestigeous districts of Rome- Borgese park. It is just few steps walk from Spanish steps and Via Veneto. There is a private park, swimming pool and restaurant with panoramic view. It is a family managed hotel, was rennovated in 2004</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel de Russie</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via del Babuino, 9</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelderussie.it\"><span>www.hotelderussie.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This hotel is located in the centre of Rome, Piazza del Popolo and Spanish steps are. It&nbsp;was the prefered place of Russian aristocracy in XIX century. It combines great style with professional service. Managed by Rocco Forte.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hassler Roma</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Piazza della Trinita dei Monti,6</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelhasslerroma.com\"><span>www.hotelhasslerroma.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>It is the unique hotel, open up in 1885. Considered to be the most prestigeous in Rome. Located on top of Spanish Steps, next to Borgese Park. Interior in very elegant and chic.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended 4* hotels:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Imperiale</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Vittorio Veneto, 24</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelimperialeroma.it\"><span>www.hotelimperialeroma.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Elegant and cosy hotel built up at the end of 1800. Located in 5 storey building of XIX century on Via Veneto street. Was recently restored.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ludovisi Palace</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Ludovisi,43</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.ludovisipalacehotel.com\"><span>www.ludovisipalacehotel.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located on Via Ludovisi, near Via Veneto. Just few minutes from Villa Borgese and Spanish Steps. It has 57 comfortable rooms decorated with elegant taste.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Cicerone</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Cicerone, 55/c</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelciceronerome.com\"><span>www.hotelciceronerome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Cicerone hotel is located in one of the most prestigeous districts of Rome, few steps from Piazza del Popolo, Piazza Navona and Vatican. It has 287 standard rooms, 5 superior and 10 suites. All rooms were recently rennovated, well equiped with amenities. Rooms are very spacious. Suites have separate sleeping and dining room.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Visconti Palace</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Federico Cesi, 37</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.viscontipalace.com/\"><span>www.viscontipalace.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This hotel is located on the side of Tiber river where Vatican is located. 15 minutes walk from Piazza del Popolo, Piazza di spagna and Piazza Navona. There are 247 rooms, including 13 appartments. Modern interiors, bright colours make this hotel special and cosy. There are all necessary modern conveniences and amenities. Internet WI FI connection.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">White Hotel</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via in Arcione, 77</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.whitehotel.com\"><span>www.whitehotel.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is situated in the building of XIX century in the center of Rome. Just 100 metres from Trevi fountain. It was open in 1993 and was restored several times. There is a small Cigar Bar that offers guests variuos drinks and snacks and also excellent choice of sigars and tobacco. There is evening music in lobby bar.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Savoy</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Ludovisi, 15</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.savoy.it\"><span>www.savoy.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel has excellent position - near Via Veneto in the centre of Rome, just few steps from Spanish Steps and Villa Borgese. Rooms are decorated in classical style. Elegant furniture and comfortable&nbsp;colours will make your stay a pleasant one.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Commodore</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Torino, 1</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelcommodore.com\"><span>www.hotelcommodore.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is located in the centre of Rome near Opera and Santa Maria Maggiore Basilica. Near Termini railway station that makes it easier for you if you travel by train to other cities. Comfortable and quiet hotel. Classical Italian interiors.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Grand Hotel Hermitage</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via E. Vajna, 12/18</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.grandhotelhermitageroma.it\"><span>www.grandhotelhermitageroma.it</span></a>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located in the most elegant residential district of Rome - Parioli. Very popular among businessman and tourists. There is a small cosy lobby bar where you can taste cocktails. Very beautiful roof garden with panoramic city view.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Stendhal</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via del Tritone, 113</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelstendhalrome.com\"><span>www.hotelstendhalrome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located in the centre of Rome, near Spanish steps, Piazza Barberini and Trevi Fountain. Via Condotti famous for its boutiques and restaurants is also near. It has elegant design.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended 3* hotels:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Accademia</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Piazza Accademia di San Luca, 74</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.accademiahotel.com/\"><span>www.accademiahotel.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located in the centre of Rome, 100 metres from Trevi Fountain and Spanish Steps.&nbsp;There are&nbsp;Via Condotti and Via Veneto near it - nice area for shopping. Also, few steps from Pantheon, Quirinale, Navona Square and Colosseo.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Diplomatic</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Vittoria Colonna, 28</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hoteldiplomatic.it\"><span>www.hoteldiplomatic.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The building itself was built in 1890 in Umbertino style. In 2001 there was done a big restauration. It is popular among tourists and businessman. Located close to Vatican. 20 minutes walk up to Spanish steps and Trevi Fountain.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Caprice</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Liguria, 38</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelcaprice.com\"><span>www.hotelcaprice.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located in the traditional Italian Palace. The building was built in 1800. Fully renewed. Located 30 metres from Via Veneto on one of the most elegant streets of Rome. There are many elegant restaurants and clubs near by.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Priscilla</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Calabria, 17</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelpriscillarome.com\"><span>www.hotelpriscillarome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located inside the building of XIX century. Close to Via Veneto - street of restaurants and boutiques.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Viminale</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via C. Balbo, 31</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.viminale.hotelinrome.com/\"><span>www.viminale.hotelinrome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located in the centre of Rome, not far from Basilica Santa Maria Maggiore, Colosseo, Imperial Forums, Trevi Fountain and Spanish Steps. There is a large terrace with panoramic view to Eternal city.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Quattro Fontane</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via delle Quattro Fontane 149/A</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotel4fontane.com\"><span>www.hotel4fontane.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located inside the historic building of 1800, 5 minutes walk from Piazza Barberini and Trevi fountain. Was fully renewed. Really comfortable and modern interior.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended mini hotels and Bed and Breakfast:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">H2000Roma</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via delle Quattro Fontane, 16</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.h2000roma.it\"><span>www.h2000roma.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel H2000 Roma is located inside the builing of XIX century, just 2 minutes walk up to Trevi fountain, in the heart of Rome. Spanish Steps and Via Veneto - shopping and restaurant areas are 10 minutes walk from this hotel. Really a comfortable position to enjoy your visit to Rome! Very spacious rooms , all modern equiped. Some rooms with jacuzzi. Internet Wi Fi connection.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Orlanda</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Principe Amedeo, 76</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelorlanda.com/\"><span>www.hotelorlanda.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>A small hotel comfortably located in the centre of Rome, near Termini station and main attractions. Comfortable and cosy.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">B&amp;B Trevi Rome</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via&nbsp;del Lavatore, 83</span><br /><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelromeresidenzatrevi.com\"><span>www.hotelromeresidenzatrevi.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This hotel was open in 2006. Very comfortable location in the centre of Rome, 5 minutes walk from Trevi, Panteon, Spanish steps and Venitian square.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Fellini B&amp;B</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Rasella, 55</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.fellinibnb.com\"><span>www.fellinibnb.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Spent your Roman holidays in this comfortable mini hotel. Just few steps up to main Roman sightes.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">B&amp;B Vaticanstpeter</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Gregorio VII,90</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.bbvaticanstpeter.com\"><span>www.bbvaticanstpeter.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This mini hotel has just 3 rooms. Located near Vatican and St. Angel Castle.</span></div>','images/Tintoretto_1_3.jpg');
