INSERT INTO `django_flatpage` VALUES (358,'/hotels','Hotels','hotel',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(359,'/restaurant_1','Restaurants','<div>There is really a great choise of restaurants in Rome! There are pizzeria, trattoria, restaurants, wine houses where you can dine and wine. Wine houses work from 12.00 till late evening. Pizzeria and restaurants are open from 12.30 till 15.00 and from 19.30 till 23.30. Some restaurants are closed on Monday.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>One should definitely try real Italian pasta. There are so many different types of it! There are different types of sauces and cheese that go with different types of pasta. Of course, Italy is famous for wine! House wine is very common but also such types as Chianti, Montalcino, Montepulciano and many others. Wines from north of Italy are considered to be of very high class.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>From non alcoholic drinks Italians prefer spremuta (fresh orange juice) and granita - ice with fruit syrup.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>From deserts there are popular sorbets and tiramisu.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Tips are common in the restaurants. Usual tip amount is 7% from total bill.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Important! It is not permitted to smoke in restaurants. Fine is 500 euro!&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Restaurants in Rome</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ciao Bella </span>( Via Vittorio Veneto, 12 Roma)</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Traditional Roman cuisine. Mostly fish dishes, but also meat, pizza, deserts. It is a cosy restaurant in the centre of Rome. Popular for tourists. Average meal cost - 37 euro per person. Open every day. 12.30 - 15.00, 19.00 - 24.00. Reservation is needed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.ciaobellaristorante.com/\"><span>www.ciaobellaristorante.com</span></a></div>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Tuna Restaurant </span>(Via Veneto, 11) Tel. <span style=\"font-weight: normal;\" dir=\"ltr\">+39 06 4201 6531 </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\" dir=\"ltr\">It is a new fish restaurant open in 2008. Romantic interior for candle light dinner. Any type of fresh fish, seafood, exellent selection of wine and unique deserts. Average cost - 50 euro per person. Reservation is needed.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.tunaroma.it/\"><span>www.tunaroma.it</span></a></p>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Da Gianni al Cacio &amp; Pepe</span> (Via Avezzana, 11) Tel.+39 06 3217268&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Cosy family restaurant where you can enjoy classical Italian meal. Terrace is open in summer time. Average meal cost - 15 euro per person excluding wine. Open from 12.00 till 15.00, 18.30 - 23.00 from monday till friday, 12.00 - 15.00 - on saturday. Reservation needed</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.magnabene.com/\"><span>www.magnabene.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Al Regno di Re Ferdinando</span> (Via di Monte Testaccio, 39) Tel. +39 06 5783725&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Restaurant of Naple cuisine. Pizzeria. It is located inside the beautiful palace in Testaccio district. Offers vast selection of dishes: polenta, pizzelle, arancini. Specialities: sartu di riso and gnocchi alla sorrentina. Exellent pizzas and deserts. Good selection of wine. Average cost - 25 euro per person. Open every day 12.00 - 15.00, 19.00 - 00.30. Reservation is needed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.magnabene.com/\"><span>www.magnabene.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">La Bomboniera </span>(Via Albano, 9 Roma) Tel. +39 06 789707&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">A very popular small cosy restaurant. Wonderful pasta selection. Exellent wine and desert choice. Average cost - 15 euro per person excluding wine. Open 12.00 - 15.00, 19.00 - 23.00 from monday till saturday. Reservation is needed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.2spaghi.it/roma/la-bomboniera\"><span>www.2spaghi.it/roma/la-bomboniera</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Romolo Nel Giardino Dalla Fornarina </span>(<span dir=\"ltr\">Via di Porta Settimiana, 8) Tel. +39 06 581 8284 </span></div>\r\n<div><span dir=\"ltr\">This family type restaurant is located in the middle of Trastevere district where you can feel the real Roman atmosphere. Exellent choice of pasta, fish and meat dishes and home made deserts. Average cost - 35 euro per person excluding wine</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.ristorantefornarina.it/\"><span>www.ristorantefornarina.it</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Il Convivio </span>(Via dei Soldati, 28) Tel. +39 06 68805950</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Elegant atmosphere for a Italian meal</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.ilconviviotroiani.com/\"><span>www.ilconviviotroiani.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ristorante Il Caminetto</span> (Viale Dei Parioli, 89) ?el.+39&nbsp;06 8083946</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Traditional Roman cuisine in the most elegant residential district of Rome -Parioli. Average cost - 40 euro per person including wine. Reservation is needed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.caminettoroma.it/\"><span>www.caminettoroma.it</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">La Pergola</span> (Via Cadlolo, 101) Tel: +39 06 35092055</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">This is Michelin restaurant. It is located on the last floor of Cavalieri Hilton hotel. Wonderful panoramic view. Fish and meat cuisine.</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.romacavalieri.it/\"><span>www.romacavalieri.it</span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">La Rosetta</span> (Panteon area) via della rosetta, 8. Tel +39 06 6861002</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">One of the most prestigious restaurants in Rome that offers fish cuisine&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.larosetta.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>www.larosetta.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">La Margutta</span> ( Via Margutta, 118) Tel. +39 06 32650577</div>\r\n<div>Vegetarian restaurant on one of quiet Roman streets, just few steps from Spanish steps.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.ilmargutta.it\"><span>www.ilmargutta.it</span></a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Sapore di Mare</span></div>\r\n<div>Via del Pie di Marmo, 36 Roma 3392329358- Govanni</div>\r\n<div>Really wonderful fish restaurant with all types of fish - from lobstres to oysters. Always fresh fish on ice! Special wine selection.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.saporedimarearoma.it\">www.saporedimarearoma.it</a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Pierluigi Ristorante</span></div>\r\n<div>Piazza de ricci, 144, Roma. 06 6861302</div>\r\n<div>Located in the centre of rome. Traditional Roman cuisine and fish specialities.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.pierluigi.it\">www.pierluigi.it</a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Bars and restaurants with life music</span></div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Alexander Platz</span></p>\r\n<div>Musica jazz&nbsp;<br />Via Ostia 9<br /><a href=\"http://www.alexanderplatz.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>alexanderplatz.it</span></a><br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Alpheus<br /></span>Musica soul, rock&nbsp;<br />Via del Commercio 36&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.alpheus.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>alpheus.it </span></a><br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Auditorium Parco della Musica</span> <br />Musica pop, soul, rock, d\'autore <br />Viale Pietro De Coubertin&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.auditorium.com/\" target=\"new window\"><span>auditorium.com </span></a><br /><br /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Big Mama</span><br />Blues, jazz, funky<br />Via S.Francesco a Ripa 18&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.bigmama.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>bigmama.it</span></a><br /><br /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Charity Cafe</span><a name=\"#charitycaf&eacute;\"></a><br />jazz blues&nbsp;<br />Via Panisperna 68&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.charitycafe.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>charitycafe.it </span></a><br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Circolo degli Artisti</span><a name=\"#circolodegliartisti\"></a><br />musica rock, fusion, indie, elettronica&nbsp;<br />Via Casilina Vecchia 42<br /><a href=\"http://www.circoloartisti.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>circoloartisti.it </span></a></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Fonclea</span><br />jazz, soul, funk, rock<br />Via Crescenzio 82a&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.fonclea.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>fonclea.it </span></a></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Gregory\'s life Jazz and Diners Club</span></div>\r\n<p>jazz tradizionale con dixieland, bebop, swing&nbsp;<br />Via Gregoriana 54d <br /><a href=\"http://www.gregorysjazzclub.com/\" target=\"new window\"><span>gregoryjazzclub.com </span></a><br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Stazione Birra</span><br />musica rock<br />Via Placanica 172. Morena Ciampino&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"http://www.stazionebirra.it/\" target=\"new window\"><span>stazionebirra.it</span></a><br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">The Place <br /></span>musica jazz, blues, R\'n\'B <br />Via Alberico II 27<br /> <a href=\"http://www.theplace.it/\"><span>theplace.it </span></a></p>',0,'',0),(349,'/transport','Transport','transport',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(350,'/reccomendation_1','Jack and Judy Corney','<p>Just came back from a wonderful visit to Rome. Wish to thank our tour guide Olga for so interesting and enjoyable tours in this wonderful city. Planning to be again back in one year.&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(351,'/reccomendation_2','Pereira family','<p>Our visit to Italy was planned well in advance and we corresponded with tour guide Olga about all our trip planning. She gave us wonderful advices on themed tours in Rome that we booked - Catacombs of Rome was just a marvelous tour. Also, she arranged for us visits to FlorencÐµ and Venice that were all wonderful. Thanks a lot!</p>',0,'',0),(352,'/reccomendation_3','Viktor Brown','<p>We were visiting Italy in March 2012. Just 2 days is not enough for a visit in Rome. However we took an all day 6 hours tour with Olga and thanks to her professionalism managed to see all important sights. Hope to come back again soon.&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(353,'/reccomendation_4','Helen Shark','<p>Me and my daughter were on a nice individual city tour with Olga. Thanks for interesting and involving explanations! See you soon. Helen</p>',0,'',0),(354,'/reccomendations','Reccomendations','reccomendation',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(355,'/flight_1','Airlines','<div>Take any airline of your preference to arrive to Rome!</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Alitalia</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.alitalia.com/\"><span>www.alitalia.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Lufthansa</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.lufthansa.com/\"><span>www.lufthansa.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Air France</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.airfrance.com/\"><span>www.airfrance.com</span></a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Have a look on special offers!</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span class=\"f\"><cite><span style=\"color: #0e774a;\"><a href=\"http://www.aviasales.ru/\"><span>www.aviasales.ru</span></a></span></cite></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span class=\"f\"><cite><span><span class=\"f\"><cite><a href=\"http://www.tripadvisor.ru/\"><span>www.tripadvisor.ru</span></a></cite></span></span></cite></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><cite><a href=\"http://www.skyexpress.ru/\"><span>www.skyexpress.ru</span></a></cite></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>',0,'',0),(356,'/flights','Flights','flight',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(357,'/hotel_1','Hotels in Rome','<div><span>You can book hotel of any category with us. Below are indicated rates for hotels in different seasons</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for 5* hotel - from 500 euro to 250 euro per room per night</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for 4* hotel - from 300 euro to 200 euro per room per night</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for 3* hotel - from 200 euro to 150 euro per room per night</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Rate for mini hotels and appartment rent - from 150 euro to 80 euro per night</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>High season in Rome: 1 March - 30 October</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended 5* hotels:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">The Westin Excelsior </span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Veneto, 125</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.excelsior.hotelinroma.com/\"><span>www.excelsior.hotelinroma.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel Westin Exelsior in&nbsp;Rome has the reputation of a fantastic place. It has famous Doney restaurant. There is the fitness centre and&nbsp;also massage centre.&nbsp;The location is on legendary Via Veneto just few steps from Piazza di Spagna and Villa Borgese</span></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"IT\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Majestic Roma </span></span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Vittorio Veneto, 50</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelmajestic.com\"><span>www.hotelmajestic.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>One of the best hotels located on Via Veneto. It was open in 1889 next to Villa Ludovisi palace. Just few steps walk to Villa Borgese, Spanish steps, via Condotti with elegant shops</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Splendid Royal</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via di Porta Pinciana, 14</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.splendidroyal.com/\"><span>www.splendidroyal.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>It is a boutique hotel located in wonderful historic place that was built in 1880. Near the prestigious district of Via Veneto and Spanish steps, near Villa Borgese park. Very elegant interior with fire places, antique furniture and original paintings. Mosaic marble floor, chandeliers, flowers make a really special atmosphere of this hotel. Mirabelle restaurant is the Michelin restaurant</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Rome Cavalieri Hilton </span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Cadlolo,101</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.romecavalieri.com\"><span>www.romecavalieri.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Location of the hotel is very special - few minutes trip from Piazza di Spagna district. It is located 35 kilometres from Fiumicino airport. The hotel is located on top of Monte Mario hill - with unique view to all Rome. There is huge spa centre and swimming pool.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Grand Hotel Parco dei Principi </span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Frescobalsi,5</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.parcodeiprincipi.com\"><span>www.parcodeiprincipi.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is located in the Villa Borgese area, 10 minutes walk from Via Veneto. It was recently restored. Pauline Borgese restaurant is considered to be one of the best in Rome</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Aldrovandi Palace Hotel</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Ulisse Aldrovandi, 15</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.aldrovandi.com\"><span>www.aldrovandi.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is located in one of most prestigeous districts of Rome- Borgese park. It is just few steps walk from Spanish steps and Via Veneto. There is a private park, swimming pool and restaurant with panoramic view. It is a family managed hotel, was rennovated in 2004</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel de Russie</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via del Babuino, 9</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelderussie.it\"><span>www.hotelderussie.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This hotel is located in the centre of Rome, Piazza del Popolo and Spanish steps are. It&nbsp;was the prefered place of Russian aristocracy in XIX century. It combines great style with professional service. Managed by Rocco Forte.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hassler Roma</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Piazza della Trinita dei Monti,6</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelhasslerroma.com\"><span>www.hotelhasslerroma.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>It is the unique hotel, open up in 1885. Considered to be the most prestigeous in Rome. Located on top of Spanish Steps, next to Borgese Park. Interior in very elegant and chic.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended 4* hotels:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Imperiale</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Vittorio Veneto, 24</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelimperialeroma.it\"><span>www.hotelimperialeroma.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Elegant and cosy hotel built up at the end of 1800. Located in 5 storey building of XIX century on Via Veneto street. Was recently restored.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ludovisi Palace</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Ludovisi,43</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.ludovisipalacehotel.com\"><span>www.ludovisipalacehotel.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located on Via Ludovisi, near Via Veneto. Just few minutes from Villa Borgese and Spanish Steps. It has 57 comfortable rooms decorated with elegant taste.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Cicerone</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Cicerone, 55/c</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelciceronerome.com\"><span>www.hotelciceronerome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Cicerone hotel is located in one of the most prestigeous districts of Rome, few steps from Piazza del Popolo, Piazza Navona and Vatican. It has 287 standard rooms, 5 superior and 10 suites. All rooms were recently rennovated, well equiped with amenities. Rooms are very spacious. Suites have separate sleeping and dining room.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Visconti Palace</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Federico Cesi, 37</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.viscontipalace.com/\"><span>www.viscontipalace.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This hotel is located on the side of Tiber river where Vatican is located. 15 minutes walk from Piazza del Popolo, Piazza di spagna and Piazza Navona. There are 247 rooms, including 13 appartments. Modern interiors, bright colours make this hotel special and cosy. There are all necessary modern conveniences and amenities. Internet WI FI connection.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">White Hotel</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via in Arcione, 77</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.whitehotel.com\"><span>www.whitehotel.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is situated in the building of XIX century in the center of Rome. Just 100 metres from Trevi fountain. It was open in 1993 and was restored several times. There is a small Cigar Bar that offers guests variuos drinks and snacks and also excellent choice of sigars and tobacco. There is evening music in lobby bar.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Savoy</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Ludovisi, 15</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.savoy.it\"><span>www.savoy.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel has excellent position - near Via Veneto in the centre of Rome, just few steps from Spanish Steps and Villa Borgese. Rooms are decorated in classical style. Elegant furniture and comfortable&nbsp;colours will make your stay a pleasant one.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Hotel Commodore</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Torino, 1</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelcommodore.com\"><span>www.hotelcommodore.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The hotel is located in the centre of Rome near Opera and Santa Maria Maggiore Basilica. Near Termini railway station that makes it easier for you if you travel by train to other cities. Comfortable and quiet hotel. Classical Italian interiors.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Grand Hotel Hermitage</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via E. Vajna, 12/18</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.grandhotelhermitageroma.it\"><span>www.grandhotelhermitageroma.it</span></a>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located in the most elegant residential district of Rome - Parioli. Very popular among businessman and tourists. There is a small cosy lobby bar where you can taste cocktails. Very beautiful roof garden with panoramic city view.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Stendhal</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via del Tritone, 113</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelstendhalrome.com\"><span>www.hotelstendhalrome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located in the centre of Rome, near Spanish steps, Piazza Barberini and Trevi Fountain. Via Condotti famous for its boutiques and restaurants is also near. It has elegant design.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended 3* hotels:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Accademia</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Piazza Accademia di San Luca, 74</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.accademiahotel.com/\"><span>www.accademiahotel.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located in the centre of Rome, 100 metres from Trevi Fountain and Spanish Steps.&nbsp;There are&nbsp;Via Condotti and Via Veneto near it - nice area for shopping. Also, few steps from Pantheon, Quirinale, Navona Square and Colosseo.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Diplomatic</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Vittoria Colonna, 28</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hoteldiplomatic.it\"><span>www.hoteldiplomatic.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>The building itself was built in 1890 in Umbertino style. In 2001 there was done a big restauration. It is popular among tourists and businessman. Located close to Vatican. 20 minutes walk up to Spanish steps and Trevi Fountain.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Caprice</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Liguria, 38</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelcaprice.com\"><span>www.hotelcaprice.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Located in the traditional Italian Palace. The building was built in 1800. Fully renewed. Located 30 metres from Via Veneto on one of the most elegant streets of Rome. There are many elegant restaurants and clubs near by.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Priscilla</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Calabria, 17</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelpriscillarome.com\"><span>www.hotelpriscillarome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located inside the building of XIX century. Close to Via Veneto - street of restaurants and boutiques.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Viminale</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via C. Balbo, 31</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.viminale.hotelinrome.com/\"><span>www.viminale.hotelinrome.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located in the centre of Rome, not far from Basilica Santa Maria Maggiore, Colosseo, Imperial Forums, Trevi Fountain and Spanish Steps. There is a large terrace with panoramic view to Eternal city.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Quattro Fontane</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via delle Quattro Fontane 149/A</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotel4fontane.com\"><span>www.hotel4fontane.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel is located inside the historic building of 1800, 5 minutes walk from Piazza Barberini and Trevi fountain. Was fully renewed. Really comfortable and modern interior.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Recommended mini hotels and Bed and Breakfast:</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">H2000Roma</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via delle Quattro Fontane, 16</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.h2000roma.it\"><span>www.h2000roma.it</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Hotel H2000 Roma is located inside the builing of XIX century, just 2 minutes walk up to Trevi fountain, in the heart of Rome. Spanish Steps and Via Veneto - shopping and restaurant areas are 10 minutes walk from this hotel. Really a comfortable position to enjoy your visit to Rome! Very spacious rooms , all modern equiped. Some rooms with jacuzzi. Internet Wi Fi connection.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Orlanda</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Principe Amedeo, 76</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelorlanda.com/\"><span>www.hotelorlanda.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>A small hotel comfortably located in the centre of Rome, near Termini station and main attractions. Comfortable and cosy.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">B&amp;B Trevi Rome</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via&nbsp;del Lavatore, 83</span><br /><span><a href=\"http://www.hotelromeresidenzatrevi.com\"><span>www.hotelromeresidenzatrevi.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This hotel was open in 2006. Very comfortable location in the centre of Rome, 5 minutes walk from Trevi, Panteon, Spanish steps and Venitian square.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Fellini B&amp;B</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Rasella, 55</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.fellinibnb.com\"><span>www.fellinibnb.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>Spent your Roman holidays in this comfortable mini hotel. Just few steps up to main Roman sightes.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">B&amp;B Vaticanstpeter</span></div>\r\n<div><span>Via Gregorio VII,90</span></div>\r\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.bbvaticanstpeter.com\"><span>www.bbvaticanstpeter.com</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>This mini hotel has just 3 rooms. Located near Vatican and St. Angel Castle.</span></div>',0,'',0),(343,'/shops','Shops','shop',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(344,'/transport_1','Fines','<p>It is necessary to say that one should definitely pay the transportation in Italy. When controlers arrive there is no way out - even if you do not have money! There is no way to negotiate the fine - it can only increase it! The fine is usually 50 euro. After paying it you will pay the usual 1 euro ticket. If you can not pay the fine right then you will get the receipt that needs to be payed to Ufficio Abbonamenti e Informazioni ATAF. If you are late for this pay you will need to pay 200 euro!</p>',0,'',0),(345,'/transport_2','Metro and buses in Rome','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">You can buy tickets for metro and bus in giornals kiosk (giornalaio) or in Tabacco store (tabacci) or inside metro mashines. Ticket is valid 75 minutes on ground trip or 1 trip on metro</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\"><strong>Types of tickets:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\"><strong>Biglietto</strong> - 1 euro, valid for 75 minutes ( 1 metro trip). During this time you can make any number of ground trips and 1 underground trip only</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\"><strong>Biglietto giornaliero o BIG</strong> - 4.10 euro can be used during all day for any number of trips in metro, bus, tram and suburban trains within the city. One should punch it&nbsp;at the first entrance and it will be valid 24 hours</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\"><strong>Biglietto turistico integrato BIT</strong> (11 EURO)- valid 3 days</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\"><strong>Carta settimanale CIS</strong> (16 EURO) - it is a personal document, valid 1 week. You will write your name, year and place of birth&nbsp;on it. When it is controlled you should present your passport or driving licence.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Roman metro</strong> - is the underground system of transportation in Rome. It was open in 1955. It consists of A (red)&nbsp;and B (blue)&nbsp;lines. Right now there are construction works to create C line (green). Metro working hours 5.30 - 23.30, saturday till 00.30</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ð¡ost of metro ticket:</strong> 1 Ðµuro<br /><strong>Cost of bus tickets:</strong> 1.20 Ðµuro, ticket is purshased inside the bus</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Travelling time from Termini to Anagnina is 20 minutes.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">From Anagnina to Ciampino travelling time is 25 minutes<br /><br /><strong>Metro&nbsp;works:</strong> 5.30-23.30, on saturday&nbsp;till 00.30 <br /><strong></strong></div>',0,'',0),(346,'/transport_3','Taxi in Rome','<p>Taxi in Rome is quite expensive. Short trips are not convenient - the first 7 kilometres will cost you not less than 4 euro and then 0, 7 euro per kilometre. On Sundays and holidays the rate is 0,6 euro per kilometre higher. Also, at night, 22.00 - 07.00 the rate wil be 2 euro higher.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Taxi</strong> from Termini to Ciampino - 35-40 Ðµuro</p>',0,'',0),(347,'/transport_4','How to reach the centre of Rome from airport Fiumicino','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"left\">Roman international airport, oficcially called Leonardo da Vinci Fiumicino consists of 3 terminals -A, B, C. International flights are received to B and C terminals. How to reach Rome from Fiumicino?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1) On express train</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">There is the express train to Termini station from Fiumicino. It goes from 6.37 till 22.52. The trip lasts 31 minutes. You will find it according to the indications Stazione FS within terminal. One trip costs 14 euro. Children below 12 years old are free. Tickets are sold at cashier desk or in mashines. Once you arrive to Termini you can walk to Metro signed if you need to take the metro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2) On the bus</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, you can take a bus from Fiumicino.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Terravision Shuttle goes every 2 hours, 8.30 - 20.30 and one trip costs 7 euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Schiaffini Travel Shuttle goes twice a day from 8.30 till 20.30 , one trip costs 8 euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cotral buses of this company run without scedule, trip will cost 5 euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3) Taxi</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Taxi from the airport will cost 45 - 50 euro</div>',0,'',0),(348,'/transport_5','How to reach the centre of Rome from Ciampino airport ','<p><strong>1) By train</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">From Termini station to Ciampino train goes every 15 - 20 minutes from 5.34 till 22.42. Trip lasts 15 minutes. You can see the scedule on Trenitalia site.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2) By bus&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">From Ciampino railway station till airport Fiumicino Schiaffini Autoline runs buses.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><strong>3) By metro and then by bus</strong></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From Anagnina railway station by A metro line there are buses from platform 1</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(334,'/note_8','Tour to Naples','<p>We arrange tours to Naples - Italian city in Campania region and archeological area of Pompei - partially buried Roman town - city that was destroyed during the eruption of mount Vesuvius in AD 79.</p>\r\n<p>Arrangment of railway tickets or transfers and visits with licenced tour guide.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(335,'/note_9','Tour to Milan. Shopping','<p>We oragnize shopping tours to Milan - centre of fashion. Visits to main boutiques and outlets. Special prices all year round. Arrangment of railway tickets or transfers and tours with licenced guides.</p>',0,'',0),(336,'/note_10','Football news','<p>As you know football occupies an important place of italian life! If you are interested in football too, we can organise <strong>tickets to stadium</strong> for you! It`s watching games on TV, at the stadium, and in the morning is cheerful, hot and colorful discussion of the results in bar with a cup of coffee! <strong>Stadium in Rome</strong> - <strong>piazzale del Foro Italico.</strong></p>',0,'',0),(337,'/notes','Notes','note',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(338,'/shop_1','SALE IN ROME','<p><strong>Saldi (sale)</strong> are starting on the first sunday of January in winter and on the first Sunday of July&nbsp;in summer. During the sales you will find discounts of 30% - 50%. It is important that on every article on sale there is indicated the initial price.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Liquidazioni</strong> - total sale that some shops do before closing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vendite Promozionali</strong> - special promotions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sconti</strong> - discounts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Entrata libera</strong> - come in to have a look.</p>',0,'',0),(339,'/shop_2','OPENING HOURS','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Usually shops are open between 09.00 - 13.00 and 15.30 - 19.30 (in summer 16.00 - 20.00). In the centre of the city some shops are open from 10.30 till 19.30. On Sundays most of the shops are closed (excluding Christmas time). August is holiday time for Italians. Most of the shops are closed for 2 -3 weeks in August. Ferragosto is celebrated on 15 August. Brand boutiques you will find in Spanish steps district - Via Condotti, Via Frattina, Via Borgognola, Via della Croce and other side streets.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, in other districts there are shops with good Italian brands - Via del Corso, Via Nazionale, Via Cola di Rienzo. Big Stores are: La Rinascente, Coin, Gallerea Alberto Sordi.</p>',0,'',0),(340,'/shop_3','CASLET ROMANO OUTLET','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Castel Romano is really the house of shops and boutiques! Here you will find articles of hiest quality from prestigeous designers, with discounts of 30% - 70%. And all this all year round. It is located at 40 minutes drive from Rome. You will be surprized by the goods represented: international brands, sport goods, accessories, leather goods. And all this just in one place! The space is 25000 m2. You will find there: Asics, Bruno Magli, Calvin Klein, Diesel, Levi\'s, Mandarina Duck, La Perla, Pal Zileri, Pinko, Puma, Reebok, Roberto Cavalli, Salvatore Ferragamo, Valentino and many others. There are many bars, restaurants, children play ground and many other conveniences. The parking is for 2000 cars and you will always find your space. Also, there is the shuttle bus that runs from Rome from Piazza Barberini.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Call 3906 3234705 to book the place one day in advance before 16.00. The price is 21 euro up and down. From monday till thursday bus runs twice a day. Departure from Piazza Barberini at 09.15 and 14.15. Departure back from Castel Romano - 13.00 and 18.00. On Saturday and sunday - once a day. From Piazza Barberini - 09.15 and back from the outlet - 13.00.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, at any hotel reception you can book your shuttle bus. You can call 39 06 37350810 or 39 3294317686 one day before the trip. Price - 25 euro up and down ticket. Outlet is open from Monday till Thursday from 10.00 till 20.00. From friday till sunday - from 10.00 till 21.00 You can see more details on <a href=\"http://www.mcarthurglen.it\">www.mcarthurglen.it</a></p>',0,'',0),(341,'/shop_4','VALMONTONE OUTLET','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Valmontone outlet is located at 40 kilometres from Rome. This is the city of shops and boutiques, where you will find GF Ferre, Baldinini, Boticelli, Gaudi, Cacharel, Pacherson, Miss Sixty, Rocco Barocco, Fellini, Pierre Cardin. You will find 30% - 70% discount on dresses, leather, children goods, accessories - all at very convenient prices. </p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"center\">Yoy can reach Valmontone by A1 road (Rome -&nbsp;Naples), uscita to Valmontone and then following signes to Outlet Fashion District.</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /></span></p>',0,'',0),(342,'/shop_5','TAX FREE','<p>In any shop you can pay by cash or credit card. IVA (VAT)&nbsp;is at 12% - for dresses and more than 30% for luxury gods. It is very conveniet to shop in the shops where you can see Tax Free sign.</p>\r\n<p>Tourists from non - european countries can return 15% of tax in the airport or in Tax Free centres in the city when exiting from Italy. Tax free is applicable when you buy for not less than 155 euro.</p>',0,'',0),(318,'/restaurants','Рестораны','restaurant',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(319,'/contact_1','Телефон','+39 3336631315',0,'',0),(320,'/contact_2','Skype','olga.gidinrome',0,'',0),(321,'/contact_3','E-mail','olga@rim-gid.com',0,'',0),(322,'/contact_4','Вконтакте','vkontakte.ru/id2981077',0,'',0),(323,'/contacts','Контакты','contact',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(324,'/italy','Другие города Италии','italy',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(325,'/fotos','Photo','foto',0,'articles/fotos.html',0),(326,'/translate','Translations','<p>Offering interpreting on seminars, events, business meetings, conferences</p>\r\n<p><strong>Experience in International events:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Railway road summit in Rome</li>\r\n<li>Conferences on medical, legal and financial subjects</li>\r\n<li>Fashion events</li>\r\n<li>Business meetings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><strong>Interpreting</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>synchro interpreting</li>\r\n<li>consequtive interpreting</li>\r\n<li>written translation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Languages: </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Italian</li>\r\n<li>English</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Rates:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Consequtive translation</strong> - 60 euro per hour</li>\r\n<li><strong>Synchro translation</strong> - 80 euro per hour</li>\r\n<li><strong>Written traslation</strong> - rate depend on the text subject</li>\r\n</ul>',0,'articles/excursion.html',0),(327,'/note_1','Exhibition in Rome','<p>Exhibition of masterpieces of Tintoretto - Italian painter of XVI entury - Scuderie del Quirinale, until 10 June. Entrance ticket - 14 euro.&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(328,'/note_2','Exhibition in Rome','<p>Salvador Dali -one of the most celebrated artists of all times - exhibition in Complesso Vittoriano, piazza Venezia. Until 1 July. Entrance ticket - 12 euro per person.</p>',0,'',0),(329,'/note_3','Tour Sale!','<p>Special Offer ! 10 % DISCOUNT on &nbsp;ALL TOURS , 15 % discount on ALL TRANSPORT SERVICES always on TUESDAY, WEDNESDAY AND THURSDAY.</p>',0,'',0),(330,'/note_4','Medici in Florence','<p>This is a themed tour in Florence. Visits to resideces and palaces connected to the history of Medici family that ruled over 3 centuries in Florence. We will also visit a family chapel - St. Laurence Basilica and New Chapel that were decored by Michelangelo. Tour lasts 4 hours. Cost - 300 euros ( 1 - 6 persons)</p>',0,'',0),(331,'/note_5','Wine tour in Tuscany','<p>This is a wonderful tour to the most pittoresque region of Italy - Tuscany. Visit to Chianti region - paradise for gourmands. This tour lasts 8 hours. We will see famous landscapes of Tuscany hills where Leonardo da Vinci was inspired when he painted Mona Lisa. We will stop by in medievil cities - Montalcino and Montepulciano. Our wine degustation will take place in various wine cellars. We will see cheese production factories where we will be able to assist to the process of production. Our lunch break will be in a locan family owned restaurant. Florentine beefsteak is one of the speciality. Tour cost - 890 euro ( 2 - 7 persons) including transportation during the tour &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(332,'/note_6','Tour to Florence','<p>We arrange individual city and themed tours in Florence - capital of Italian region Tuscany, cradle of renaissance arts, city of Michelangelo. Arrangement of railway and car transfers and tours with licenced guide.</p>',0,'',0),(333,'/note_7','Tour to Venice ','<p>We arrance city and themed individual tours to Venice - city of arts, located on canals and sea renowned for the beaty of its settings, architecture and artworks. Arrangement of railway tickets or car transfers and visits with licenced tour guide.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',0,'',0),(316,'/hotels','Отели','hotel',0,'articles/notes.html',0),(317,'/restaurant_1','Рестораны','<div>В Риме огромные выбор ресторанов! Вы можете выбирать между пицерией, тратторией, рестораном или энотекой. Пицерии и рестораны работаютс 12.30 до 15.00 и с 19.30 до 22.30. Энотеки работают с 12.00 до поздего вечера.&nbsp;Некоторые рестораны закрыты в понедельник.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Италия знаменита пастой -<strong> pasta</strong>. Это блюдо подается как первое блюдо после закуски. &nbsp;Существует столько разновидностей этого популярного блюда! С разнами соусами и разными видами сыров. Конечно же Италия знаменита винами! Очень популярно домашнее вино и другие разновидности, например Chianti, Montalcino, Montepulciano и другие. Вина севера Италии считаются наиболее благородными.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Из&nbsp;безалкогольных напитков итальянцы предпочитают<strong> spremuta</strong> (свежевыжатый сок) и <strong>granita</strong> (лед с фруктовым сиропом)</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Из десертов популярны тирамису и сорбеты.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>В ресторанах принято оставлять чаевые. Сренний размер чаевых - 7% от суммы счета</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Очень важно! Курение запрещено в ресторанах! Штраф - 500 евро&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Рестораны в Риме</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ciao Bella </span>( Via Vittorio Veneto, 12 Roma)</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Традиционная Римская кухня. Огромный выбор рыбных и мясных блюд, пицы и десертов. Эот уютный ресторан в центре Рима. Пользуется успехом у туристов. Средняя стоимость ужина или обеда - 37 евро на человека. Открыт каждый день. 12.30 - 15.00, 19.00 - 24.00. Необходимо бронировать столик</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.ciaobellaristorante.com\">www.ciaobellaristorante.com</a></div>\r\n<h4 style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Tuna Restaurant </span>(Via Veneto, 11) Тел. <span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-weight: normal;\" dir=\"ltr\">+39 06 4201 6531&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Это новый рыбный ресторан который был открыт в 2008 году. Любой вид свежей рыбы, морепродуктов, великолепный выбор вина и уникальных десертов. Средняя стоимость - 50 евро на человека. Необходима резервация</span><br /></span><a href=\"http://www.tunaroma.it\">www.tunaroma.it</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Da Gianni al Cacio &amp; Pepe</span> (Via Avezzana, 11) Тел.+39 06 3217268&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Уютный семейный ресторан для истинно традиционнго итальянского ужина. Летом открыта терраса. Средняя стоимость ужина или обеда - 15 евро на человека (без вина). Открыт&nbsp;12.00 - 15.00, 18.30 - 23.00 c понедельника по пятницу. 12.00 - 15.00 - по субботам.&nbsp; Необходимо бронировать столик</p>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.magnabene.com\">www.magnabene.com</a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Al Regno di Re Ferdinando</span> (Via di Monte Testaccio, 39) Тел. +39 06 5783725&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Ресторан Неаполитанской кухни. Расположен в красивом квартале Рима - Testaccio. Предлагает широкий выбор блюд: polenta, pizzelle, arancini. Особые блюда: sartu di riso и gnocchi alla sorrentina. Великолепные выбор видов пицы и десертов. Хороший выбор вин. Средняя стоимость - 25 евро на человека. Открыт каждый день, 12.00 - 15.00, 19.00 - 00.30. Необходимо бронировать столик</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.magnabene.com\">www.magnabene.com</a></div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\"><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">La Bomboniera </span>(Via Albano, 9 Roma) Тел. +39 06 789707&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"vertical-align: top;\" align=\"justify\">Очень популярн